- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The modified SIFT algorithm used in the paper involves machine learning techniques such as linear regression and gradient descent. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing): The paper deals with the processing and analysis of infants' cry signals, which are signals in the time domain. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the analysis of sound signals, which are a form of multimedia.
